OL,7,FA boater who makes a living mending
OL,8,Fbicycles may be forced to stop trading
OL,9,Fby the canal authority.
OL,11,FOliver Key, 37, runs The Bike Boat on
OL,12,Fthe Kennet and Avon Canal.
OL,14,FHe moved in two and half years ago
OL,15,Fafter a career in the Army and teaches
OL,16,Fcycling skills part-time in primary
OL,17,Fschools.
