OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F436A1708330977
OL,3,CBoater forced to stop running bike
OL,4,Cfixing business from home by canal
OL,5,Cauthority
OL,7,FHe is on a six-month continuous
OL,8,Fcruising licence, supplied by the
OL,9,FCanal River Trust, and must travel a
OL,10,Frange of 20 miles within the licence
OL,11,Fperiod to meet their requirements.
OL,13,FOliver said he had moved a range of 30
OL,14,Fmiles over the past six months and so
OL,15,Fbelieved he was on course to satisfy
OL,16,Fthe CRT regulations.
OL,18,FHowever, this was not the case, and he
OL,19,Fmay have to stop trading at the end of
OL,20,FFebruary.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
