OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F436A1708330977
OL,3,CBoater forced to stop running bike
OL,4,Cfixing business from home by canal
OL,5,Cauthority
OL,7,FHe explained: "They have decided that,
OL,8,Fin their opinion, the movements of my
OL,9,Fcraft don't count as 'bonafide
OL,10,Fnavigation'.
OL,12,F"The rules are open to interpretation,
OL,13,Fbut unfortunately it's the CRT's
OL,14,Finterpretation that counts. They are
OL,15,Fnot considering that I've moved a
OL,16,Frange of 30 miles.
OL,18,F"They describe me being in Bradford-on-
OL,19,FAvon and Bath to trade as being too
OL,20,Fmuch.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
