OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F436A1708330977
OL,3,CBoater forced to stop running bike
OL,4,Cfixing business from home by canal
OL,5,Cauthority
OL,7,F"But I have spent a third of my time
OL,8,Fin the Wiltshire countryside, where
OL,9,Fthere really isn't any business, to
OL,10,Fsatisfy their requirements. That's two
OL,11,Fmonths without trading.
OL,13,F"I don't know many small businesses
OL,14,Fthat could survive without two months'
OL,15,Fincome."
OL,17,FOliver added that he had only had one
OL,18,Fmonth's notice that the movements of
OL,19,Fhis boat were unacceptable and it's
OL,20,Fleft him with only three options.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
