OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F436A1708330977
OL,3,CBoater forced to stop running bike
OL,4,Cfixing business from home by canal
OL,5,Cauthority
OL,7,F"I can either keep my business and
OL,8,Fleave my home, I can stop trading at
OL,9,Fthe end of this month and struggle to
OL,10,Fsurvive, or I can keep trading the way
OL,11,FI have been and risk losing my boat
OL,12,Ffor going against the CRT," he
OL,13,Fexplained.
OL,15,FIn response, a Canal River Trust
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "Boating businesses
OL,17,Fare great and we are keen to support
OL,18,Fthem where we can.
