OL,3,CBoater forced to stop running bike
OL,4,Cfixing business from home by canal
OL,5,Cauthority
OL,7,F"However, when someone is a roving
OL,8,Ftrader they are declaring that they
OL,9,Fwill move from place to place on a
OL,10,Fcontinuous journey.
OL,12,F"The Kennet & Avon Canal is very busy,
OL,13,Fparticularly around towns, and we need
OL,14,Fto be fair and consistent for all our
OL,15,Fboaters, providing the same guidance
OL,16,Fon what's expected under the terms of
OL,17,Ftheir licence.
